íŸ@2095a9460650224ce028c65ff4d7abf5676569f71f88d934b70573c20b62f64b⁄lTitle: title: math log
Path: Examples
Content:
Get the logarithm of 100 to the base 10.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 100 | math log 10
2.0

```
Get the log2 of a list of values.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [16 8 4] | math log 2
